T1  - Collusion via Resale
AU  - Garratt, Rodney J.
AU  - Tröger, Thomas
AU  - Zheng, Charles Z.
Y1  - 2009/07/01
PY  - 2009
DA  - 2009/07/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA7504
T2  - Econometrica
